Katame tayo? 
Assaddhiyaṁ appahāya, avadaññutaṁ appahāya, kosajjaṁ appahāya—
ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhamme appahāya abhabbo uddhaccaṁ pahātuṁ asaṁvaraṁ pahātuṁ dussilyaṁ pahātuṁ. 
