carati …pe… 
carissati, taṁ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṁ paṭivineti, appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṁ acari …pe… 
atthaṁ carati …pe… 
atthaṁ carissati, taṁ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṁ paṭivineti, 
